| PostgreSQL (Puchi) | `pg-puchi-rw.puchi-db.svc.cluster.local:5432` |
| PostgreSQL (Supertokens) | `pg-supertokens-rw.puchi-db.svc.cluster.local:5432` |
| NATS | `nats.platform.svc.cluster.local:4222` |
| Garage (S3) | `http://garage.platform.svc.cluster.local:3900` |
| Valkey/Redis | `valkey-node.platform.svc.cluster.local:6379` |
| Supertokens | `st-core-svc.puchi-infra.svc.cluster.local:3567` |
| Supertokens (alt) | `st-core.puchi-infra.svc.cluster.local:3567` |

